summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 - 6, Block 108, D.T. Denny 1st Addition, located on west side of Fairview Avenue North, between Harrison Street and Republican Street; Lots 7, 8 and 9, Block 42, Woodlawn Addition to Green Lake, located on the northwest corner of 8th Avenue Northeast and East 69th Street; and the south 10 feet of Lot 5 and all of Lot 6, Muir's Replat of Block 71, Burke's 2nd Addition, located on the east side of 35th Avenue South, between King Street and Jackson Street with respect to the Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections, numbered 2-11 and 17-9, repsectively.
